<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="34" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="5.[813,1452,327,417]" pageId="5" pageNumber="34">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[813,961,327,351]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="34">Etymology. –</emphasis>
A combination of the Latin words: “tri-” + “setosa” meaning 3 setae, a reference to the setation of the mid tibia.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
